      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Observe, moreover, that here also (comp. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Acts 8:17",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Acts 13:3",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ") the imposition of hands occurs ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "after",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " prayer,[183] and therefore it was not a mere symbolic ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "accompaniment",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " of prayer,[184] without collative import, and perhaps only a “",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "ritus ordini et decoro congruens",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "” (Calvin). Certainly its efficacy depended only on God’s bestowal, but it was associated with the act representing this bestowal as the medium of the divine communication.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "[182] See, on the imposition of hands, Bauer in the ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Stud. u. Krit.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " 1865, p. 343 ff.; Hoelemann in his ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "neue Bibelstud.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " 1866, p. 282 ff., where also the earlier literature, p. 283, is noted.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "[183] Luke has not expressed himself in some such way as this: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "καὶ ἐπιθέντες αὐτοῖς τὰς χεῖρας προσηύξαντο",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "[184] This also in opposition to Weiss, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "bibl. Theol.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " p. 144.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
